snippet.title: Alien Hominid Invasion: Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Your very own Mothership awaits! Alien Hominid Invasion will be released on November 1st for Steam, Nintendo Switch, and Xbox. 

With a newly improved Alien Hominid HD co-launching to the same platforms, both games will also be available at a discount in a special bundle!

Alien Hominid Invasion - $19.99
Alien Hominid HD - $11.99
Alien Hominid: The Extra Terrestrial Bundle - $24.99 

Wishlist Alien Hominid Invasion here: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/843200/Alien_Hominid_Invasion/

Wishlist Alien Hominid HD here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1285360/Alien_Hominid_HD/

Find fellow aliens to invade with in our official Discord server:
https://discord.gg/thebehemoth

Learn more about The Behemoth:
https://www.thebehemoth.com/

Music by Patric Catani:
https://catani-music.de/
